{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/maid-for-hire-kisah-si-miskin-dan-si-kaya-dalam-komik-lokal/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Maid for Hire, Kisah Si Miskin dan Si Kaya dalam Komik Lokal","content":"\n<p>Kisah si Miskin dan si Kaya gak cuma ada di drama Jepang atau Korea. Di komik Indonesia juga ada! Misalnya kayak komik <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Maid for Hire (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/maid-for-hire\" target=\"_blank\">Maid for Hire</a> ini. Komik satu ini bukan sembarang komik lokal biasa. Komik ini diadaptasi langsung dari cerita di Wattpad karya Melisa Oktorina (alias Demonicblackcat). </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Maid for Hire mengisahkan seorang gadis populer bernama Andrea, yang sebenarnya berasal dari keluarga miskin. Ia harus bekerja untuk mendukung keluarga dan juga menjaga status sosialnya. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"57043\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/soul-of-neko-season-4-tantangan-baru-untuk-oto/attachment/3-289/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Siapa yang akan dipilih Alec? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Alec&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/3.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/3.jpg\" alt=\"Alec\" class=\"wp-image-57043\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Siapa yang akan dipilih Alec? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Suatu hari Andrea mendapatkan pekerjaan baru sebagai pembantu rumah tangga. Namun apesnya, ia bekerja di rumah milik Alec, playboy yang pernah mencampakkan teman Andrea. Yap, ceritanya memang rada klise. Tentang kisah drama romantis antara si Miskin dan si Kaya di era modern.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/7-komik-indonesia-adaptasi-novel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"7 Komik Indonesia Adaptasi Novel Yang Wajib Kamu Tahu (opens in a new tab)\">7 Komik Indonesia Adaptasi Novel Yang Wajib Kamu Tahu</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Walaupun begitu, percaya nggak kalau cerita ini sudah dibaca lebih dari <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.wattpad.com/story/1101861-maid-for-hire\" target=\"_blank\">20 juta kali</a> di Wattpad, loh! Gak heran kalau antusiasme yang besar ini juga terbawa sampai ke versi komik. Bahkan komik romance satu ini sudah akan memasuki season ke-3nya.  </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"57042\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/soul-of-neko-season-4-tantangan-baru-untuk-oto/attachment/2-267/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Gabriel punya potensi besar buat nyingkirin Alec (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Gabriel_Maid for Hire&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/2.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/2.jpg\" alt=\"Gabriel_Maid for Hire\" class=\"wp-image-57042\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Gabriel punya potensi besar buat nyingkirin Alec (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah penantian panjang, kamu bisa kembali menyimak cerita romantis ala Andrea dan Alec. Bagaimana hubungan mereka semakin rumit.  Selain nenek Alec yang tidak merestui hubungan mereka. Kehadiran Cindy juga semakin mempersulit. Apalagi, Gabriel juga ikut menyatakan perasaannya terhadap Andrea. Kira-kira siapa yang akan dipilih oleh Andrea? </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"57041\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/soul-of-neko-season-4-tantangan-baru-untuk-oto/attachment/1-333/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Jadi sebenarnya Cindy itu jahat atau baik? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1.jpg\" alt=\"Cindy_Maid for Hire\" class=\"wp-image-57041\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Jadi sebenarnya Cindy itu jahat atau baik? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Apakah yang akan dilakukan oleh Alec? Berhasilkan dia keluar dari bayang-bayang masa lalunya? Apakah hubungannya dengan Andrea akhirnya akan berhasil? Hmm, mungkin semua jawabannya cuma akan kamu temukan di season ke-3 ini. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/rekomendasi-komik-webtoon-romantis/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Rekomendasi Komik Webtoon Romantis di Bulan April (opens in a new tab)\">Rekomendasi Komik Webtoon Romantis di Bulan April</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Versi komik  dari Maid for Hire ini digarap oleh Erry dan Dii. Komiknya sendiri bisa kamu baca eksklusif setiap hari Sabtu di <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"CIAYO Comics (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id\" target=\"_blank\">CIAYO Comics</a>! Psst, jangan lupa dukung Andrea dan Alec di <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"CIAYO Comics Awards.  (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ciayoscope.ciayo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">CIAYO Comics Awards</a> sebagai komik romance terfavorit kamu. Siapa tau kamu jadi salah satu dari yang beruntung. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"57045\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/soul-of-neko-season-4-tantangan-baru-untuk-oto/attachment/5-280/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Confesion&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/5.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/5.jpg\" alt=\"Confesion\" class=\"wp-image-57045\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"8072f20a-610c-5323-b217-7b4444e755da"}}}